{"TopicId":217158,"ForumId":139,"TopicTitle":"A Taste of Science","CreatedByName":"Nate Simpson","CreatedById":205123,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-05-12T18:55:00Z","PageNum":6,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Meecrob","CreatedById":104543,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-05-13T16:26:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224282906\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022217158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221683994789\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002270807\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022regex\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n8 minutes ago, regex said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOkay, and? Why should I care? Go play KSP1, have fun with it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLet me be clear: I\u0027m not trying to call you out specifically. Your post just made my mind think my question. Thats why I didn\u0027t quote you. My point is more that its odd to me that there are lots of people who in 2018 would say KSP1 is their favourite game of all time, but now they are like \u0022pfft, KSP1 was some cobbled together pile of crap.\u0022 There is a reason we are all here on this board and it wasn\u0027t because KSP1 was some disaster of a game.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt makes me sad that for such a niche game, people are actively destroying the legacy the game has. If the game was so bad, why would Take Two purchase the IP? If the game was so bad, why aren\u0027t people saying \u0022oh hey, play simple rockets/JUNO\u0022 but instead they say play KSP1.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222023-05-13T16:30:38Z\u0022 title=\u002205/13/2023 04:30  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00221 yr\u0022\u003EMay 13, 2023\u003C/time\u003E by Meecrob\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Bej Kerman","CreatedById":182413,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-05-13T16:29:11Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224282912\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022217158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221683995174\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022104543\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Meecrob\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, Meecrob said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere is a reason we are all here on this board and it wasn\u0027t because KSP1 was some disaster of a game.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf KSP 1 wasn\u0027t a disaster, there would not be any need for a KSP 2.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224282912\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022217158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221683995174\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022104543\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Meecrob\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, Meecrob said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMy point is more that its odd to me that there are lots of people who in 2018 would say KSP1 is their favourite game of all time, but now they are like \u0022pfft, KSP1 was some cobbled together pile of crap.\u0022\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nKSP 1 had no competition and there were no games like it. If you only have one object in a set, you can\u0027t really say it\u0027s the worst in its own set until a better thing joins it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Alexoff","CreatedById":145774,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-05-13T16:31:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224282909\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022217158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221683994933\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022182413\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Bej Kerman\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n6 minutes ago, Bej Kerman said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s an inconsequential feature and the amount of people who regularly enjoy it as more than a novelty is greatly overstated.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nApproximately as well as multiplayer with interstellar flights. Many have said that they are not going to pursue a career in multiplayer. And interstellar flights are not much different from flights to Jool. As far as I remember, most players do not fly further than Dune.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224282914\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022217158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221683995351\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022182413\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Bej Kerman\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 minutes ago, Bej Kerman said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf KSP 1 wasn\u0027t a disaster, there would not be any need for a KSP 2\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAre you talking about that game that has sold 5 million copies and has a great steam rating?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Meecrob","CreatedById":104543,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-05-13T16:32:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/182413-bej-kerman/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022182413\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/182413-bej-kerman/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Bej Kerman\u003C/a\u003EAre you serious? The fact there is a second version of something means the first one was bad?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI feel that you are purposefully missing my point.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222023-05-13T16:35:16Z\u0022 title=\u002205/13/2023 04:35  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00221 yr\u0022\u003EMay 13, 2023\u003C/time\u003E by Meecrob\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"PDCWolf","CreatedById":58026,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-05-13T16:34:33Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224282916\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022217158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221683995474\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022145774\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Alexoff\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, Alexoff said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nApproximately as well as multiplayer with interstellar flights. Many have said that they are not going to pursue a career in multiplayer. And interstellar flights are not much different from flights to Jool. As far as I remember, most players do not fly further than Dune.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nStatistically, most players don\u0027t leave the Kerbin-Mun-Minmus system. This was evaluated some years ago.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224282914\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022217158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221683995351\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022182413\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Bej Kerman\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 minutes ago, Bej Kerman said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf KSP 1 wasn\u0027t a disaster, there would not be any need for a KSP 2.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nComedy award right here.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Alexoff","CreatedById":145774,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-05-13T16:37:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDid anyone promise steam achievements? It would be interesting to see what proportion of players reach which planet. Or is it also an unnecessary feature that no one needs?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Scarecrow71","CreatedById":210112,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-05-13T16:40:11Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224282920\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022217158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221683995823\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022145774\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Alexoff\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, Alexoff said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDid anyone promise steam achievements? It would be interesting to see what proportion of players reach which planet. Or is it also an unnecessary feature that no one needs?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI don\u0027t know if that\u0027s a necessary feature, but it would be nifty to see what percaentage of players actually go to other planets.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"regex","CreatedById":70807,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-05-13T16:43:23Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224282912\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022217158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221683995174\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022104543\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Meecrob\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n15 minutes ago, Meecrob said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThats why I didn\u0027t quote you.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWell, maybe next time don\u0027t actually quote me.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224282912\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022217158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221683995174\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022104543\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Meecrob\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n15 minutes ago, Meecrob said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMy point is more that its odd to me that there are lots of people who in 2018 would say KSP1 is their favourite game of all time\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI have never said this.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224282912\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022217158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221683995174\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022104543\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Meecrob\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n15 minutes ago, Meecrob said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nbut now they are like \u0022pfft, KSP1 was some cobbled together pile of crap.\u0022\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI have always criticized Squad for their lack of planning and direction in terms of gameplay. I have always been critical of their lack of a roadmap.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224282912\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022217158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221683995174\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022104543\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Meecrob\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n15 minutes ago, Meecrob said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere is a reason we are all here on this board and it wasn\u0027t because KSP1 was some disaster of a game.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI have never said KSP1 was a \u0022disaster\u0022.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Meecrob","CreatedById":104543,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-05-13T16:47:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/70807-regex/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002270807\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/70807-regex/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@regex\u003C/a\u003EIf I did quote you, I feel stupid. I meant to not quote you, so I apologize that i did. It was my mistake.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe rest of what I said was NOT aimed at you. You don\u0027t need to itemize what I said and attack my points. I mean its a free country, so do what you want, but I\u0027m not trying to specifically attack you. I was saying in general that there are some themes that keep being presented and I was questioning those themes, not you.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEdit to ruin my non-existant credibility: Its funny seeing who comes out of the woodwork to to tell me I\u0027m wrong when I wasn\u0027t trying to talk to them in the first place. Many people have taken up the point that KSP1 sucks hardcore and we should be glad KSP2 exists. I disagree. I\u0027m happy to discuss this in a format that does not involve personal attacks.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEdit 2: The fact that we are discussing such menial tings means that KSP2 has nothing positive to discuss, or we would be discussing it. I mean that in the best of ways. It feels like being disappointed at your kid at this point...I\u0027m not even mad. I just want the best for this franchise and when I see things that actively erode that, I say things.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222023-05-13T17:06:11Z\u0022 title=\u002205/13/2023 05:06  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00221 yr\u0022\u003EMay 13, 2023\u003C/time\u003E by Meecrob\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Spicat","CreatedById":228085,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-05-13T17:07:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224282920\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022217158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221683995823\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022145774\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Alexoff\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n25 minutes ago, Alexoff said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDid anyone promise steam achievements? It would be interesting to see what proportion of players reach which planet. Or is it also an unnecessary feature that no one needs?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYes but you will need to wait for the full release, here are CMs answer on the discord:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022jvqpFYU.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002218.73\u0022 height=\u0022127\u0022 width=\u0022678\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/jvqpFYU.png\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u00227Q1A8m2.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002215.29\u0022 height=\u0022102\u0022 width=\u0022667\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/7Q1A8m2.png\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022K6VDbxF.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002215.83\u0022 height=\u002288\u0022 width=\u0022556\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/K6VDbxF.png\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"LoSBoL","CreatedById":174038,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-05-13T17:26:43Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224282918\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022217158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221683995576\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022104543\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Meecrob\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n47 minutes ago, Meecrob said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/182413-bej-kerman/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022182413\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/182413-bej-kerman/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Bej Kerman\u003C/a\u003EAre you serious? The fact there is a second version of something means the first one was bad?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI feel that you are purposefully missing my point.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFor me personally, and I think for quite a few others the cobbled together KSP1, which I enjoyed by the way, was the reason to yearn for a KSP2.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNow I hear quite a lot (due to KSP2) that KSP1 is bug and glitchfree. Which it wasn\u0027t and isn\u0027t.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWith that said, KSP2 had got a long way to go to where it needs to be. We got time, even if people demand it now, they too have time.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Meecrob","CreatedById":104543,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-05-13T17:34:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224282939\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022217158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221683998803\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022174038\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022LoSBoL\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n10 minutes ago, LoSBoL said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFor me personally, and I think for quite a few others the cobbled together KSP1, which I enjoyed by the way, was the reason to yearn for a KSP2.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNow I hear quite a lot (due to KSP2) that KSP1 is bug and glitchfree. Which it wasn\u0027t and isn\u0027t.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWith that said, KSP2 had got a long way to go to where it needs to be. We got time, even if people demand it now, they too have time.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI see what you are getting at, and I\u0027ll gladly admit that KSP1 was not some AAA polished experience. What I am getting at is there seems to be this sentiment of you have to be in one camp or the other: KSP1 or KSP2, and I think that is a silly thought. There are obvious differences with the development of both games and to compare them seems to be lacking intellectually.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEdit: In any case, I have de-railed this thread enough, sorry about that.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222023-05-13T17:38:36Z\u0022 title=\u002205/13/2023 05:38  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00221 yr\u0022\u003EMay 13, 2023\u003C/time\u003E by Meecrob\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"cocoscacao","CreatedById":225696,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-05-13T17:43:27Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224282897\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022217158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221683994225\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002258026\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022PDCWolf\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, PDCWolf said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo... now we casually sweep the \u0022interactable\u0022 part under the rug? Again?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIs this game done?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"PDCWolf","CreatedById":58026,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-05-13T17:58:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224282944\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022217158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221683999807\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022225696\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022cocoscacao\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n12 minutes ago, cocoscacao said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIs this game done?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat point are you even trying to make?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Alexoff","CreatedById":145774,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-05-13T18:12:17Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224282939\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022217158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221683998803\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022174038\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022LoSBoL\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n42 minutes ago, LoSBoL said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNow I hear quite a lot (due to KSP2) that KSP1 is bug and glitchfree. Which it wasn\u0027t and isn\u0027t.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWith that said, KSP2 had got a long way to go to where it needs to be.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCompared to KSP2, KSP1 has almost no bugs. Compared to DSP, there are a lot of bugs. And it seems to take too much time to go through the entire road map, we will most likely see 1.0 after HL3.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"LoSBoL","CreatedById":174038,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-05-13T18:13:57Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224282951\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022217158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221684001537\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022145774\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Alexoff\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 minutes ago, Alexoff said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCompared to KSP2, KSP1 has almost no bugs. Compared to DSP, there are a lot of bugs. And it seems to take too much time to go through the entire road map, we will most likely see 1.0 after HL3.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLike I said so I dont know why you need to repeat, see below;\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224282951\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022217158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221684001537\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022145774\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Alexoff\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 minutes ago, Alexoff said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWith that said, KSP2 had got a long way to go to where it needs to be.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWe\u0027ve got time.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222023-05-13T18:18:00Z\u0022 title=\u002205/13/2023 06:18  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00221 yr\u0022\u003EMay 13, 2023\u003C/time\u003E by LoSBoL\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Alexoff","CreatedById":145774,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-05-13T18:30:17Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224282952\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022217158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221684001637\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022174038\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022LoSBoL\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n12 minutes ago, LoSBoL said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWe\u0027ve got time.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWho are we? Are you saying that you forgive the developers for all their sins and missed deadlines? Well, it\u0027s your business, but you don\u0027t have to speak for everyone.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"LoSBoL","CreatedById":174038,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-05-13T18:31:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224282942\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022217158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221683999279\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022104543\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Meecrob\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n49 minutes ago, Meecrob said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI see what you are getting at, and I\u0027ll gladly admit that KSP1 was not some AAA polished experience. What I am getting at is there seems to be this sentiment of you have to be in one camp or the other: KSP1 or KSP2, and I think that is a silly thought. There are obvious differences with the development of both games and to compare them seems to be lacking intellectually.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEdit: In any case, I have de-railed this thread enough, sorry about that.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat sentiment is what I\u0027m seeing as well, like KSP1 is Walhalla compared to KSP2.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThey are incomparable, one is finished and the second is in Early Access. They will live side by side and won\u0027t bite each other\u00A0 for a long time to come.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPersonally I haven\u0027t touched KSP for a long time, I am enjoying KSP2, but for who doesn\u0027t (yet?), Thank God there is KSP to enjoy.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"cocoscacao","CreatedById":225696,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-05-13T18:32:45Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224282956\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022217158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221684002607\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022226561\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022GGG-GoodGuyGreg\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 minutes ago, GGG-GoodGuyGreg said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGentlemen, are you trying to get this thread locked?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMaybe get a separate \u003Cs\u003Eroom\u003C/s\u003E thread?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027d actually prefer that not to happen on official posts. Someone can simply open \u0022Doom and gloom\u0022 thread, and vent there.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222023-05-13T18:33:12Z\u0022 title=\u002205/13/2023 06:33  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00221 yr\u0022\u003EMay 13, 2023\u003C/time\u003E by cocoscacao\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"LoSBoL","CreatedById":174038,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-05-13T18:34:40Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224282957\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022217158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221684002617\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022145774\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Alexoff\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, Alexoff said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWho are we? Are you saying that you forgive the developers for all their sins and missed deadlines? Well, it\u0027s your business, but you don\u0027t have to speak for everyone.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWe is you and me in this case, and everybody else as well. You\u0027ve got time for KSP2 to be developed further, even if you personally assess current development as sins and missed deadlines. It\u0027s not like you need it to survive, I\u0027m certain I can speak for you on that matter.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Meecrob","CreatedById":104543,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-05-13T18:35:01Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224282958\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022217158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221684002668\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022174038\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022LoSBoL\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n7 hours ago, LoSBoL said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat sentiment is what I\u0027m seeing as well, like KSP1 is Walhalla compared to KSP2.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThey are incomparable, one is finished and the second is in Early Access. They will live side by side and won\u0027t bite each other\u00A0 for a long time to come.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPersonally I haven\u0027t touched KSP for a long time, I am enjoying KSP2, but for who doesn\u0027t (yet?), Thank God there is KSP to enjoy.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt boggles my mind...like nobody said GTA: San Andreas was a pile of crap when they released a new GTA....I know, I know..IV is divided, but nobody would dare say San Andreas sucks because GTA V exists.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n[snip]\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222023-05-14T01:45:45Z\u0022 title=\u002205/14/2023 01:45  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00221 yr\u0022\u003EMay 14, 2023\u003C/time\u003E by Vanamonde\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Alexoff","CreatedById":145774,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-05-13T18:41:50Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224282963\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022217158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221684002880\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022174038\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022LoSBoL\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n7 hours ago, LoSBoL said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou\u0027ve got time for KSP2 to be developed further\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI strongly doubt that in 5 years I will have the time and desire to play KSP2.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224282963\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022217158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221684002880\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022174038\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022LoSBoL\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n7 hours ago, LoSBoL said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s not like you need it to survive, I\u0027m certain I can speak for you on that matter.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOf course, otherwise the conversation would have been of a completely different nature.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n[snip]\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222023-05-14T01:49:03Z\u0022 title=\u002205/14/2023 01:49  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00221 yr\u0022\u003EMay 14, 2023\u003C/time\u003E by Vanamonde\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"cocoscacao","CreatedById":225696,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-05-13T18:50:53Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224282966\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022217158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221684003310\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022145774\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Alexoff\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n9 minutes ago, Alexoff said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI strongly doubt that in 5 years I will have the time and desire to play KSP2.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nErm... how is that relevant exactly \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:P\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:P\u0022\u003E? Imagine asking some production studio to finish last season of your favourite series one year earlier, because you might not live long enough to see it\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222023-05-13T18:52:35Z\u0022 title=\u002205/13/2023 06:52  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00221 yr\u0022\u003EMay 13, 2023\u003C/time\u003E by cocoscacao\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Alexoff","CreatedById":145774,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-05-13T18:56:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224282967\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022217158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221684003853\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022225696\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022cocoscacao\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 minutes ago, cocoscacao said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nErm... how is that relevant exactly \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:P\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:P\u0022\u003E? Imagine asking some production studio to finish last season of your favourite series one year earlier, because you might not live long enough to see it\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nImagine telling fans that a game announced for 2020 will be ready in 2028 and they\u0027re not happy! One year, 10 years - what\u0027s the difference? A hundred years, whatever! You were told to wait - so wait! It feels like I\u0027m talking to bureaucrats.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"cocoscacao","CreatedById":225696,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-05-13T19:03:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224282968\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022217158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221684004176\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022145774\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Alexoff\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n9 minutes ago, Alexoff said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou were told to wait\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou\u0027re totally free to walk away, and never think about it. Your life doesn\u0027t depend on it. Be happy.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEdit:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCheck Mount and Blade Bannerlord development. I totally forgot about that game, and bought it in a finished state, 7 years later.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222023-05-13T19:06:09Z\u0022 title=\u002205/13/2023 07:06  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00221 yr\u0022\u003EMay 13, 2023\u003C/time\u003E by cocoscacao\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"}]}